  "body": "<p>Thanks Dare for leaving this in the comments a couple Mondays ago. Couldn't resist scripting it. Also ended up posting a little <a href=\"https://instagram.com/p/4PT7ixtnvf/?taken-by=amytangerine\">hyperlapse video on Instagram</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1597363070415-8L41AEF22Q59J4C2A9I4/12a-Remember%2Bto%2Balways%2Bbe%2Byourself.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Remember to always be yourself. Unless you suck. - Joss Whedon</p><p>Hope to continue spreading more motivation for each of your Mondays this year using <a href=\"http://goo.gl/lB0K35\">this watercolor set from Michaels</a> and a brush that says Royal 2 on it (can’t remember where it’s from, sorry!). If you have a favorite quote – snarky, silly, or simple in its’ wisdom, please share in the comments!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
